value.name: Nosy Be, Madagascar: The Complete Guide - TripSavvy
value.snippet: Nosy Be is surrounded by the productive waters of the Mozambique Channel, approximately five miles from mainland Madagascar. The product of volcanic activity, it has a total area of around 120 square miles and is covered by dense rainforest, interspersed with scenic crater lakes and waterfalls.
